result.name: 心越 Le Viet’s

reviews.text:
The location of this restaurant is better go with car. The service is not so nice and friendly, waitress seems like no patient. 

The portion of the food is very very small, you can’t believe how tiny of that bowl of curry is like kid menu.  
I don’t recommend this restaurant if you want a cozy atmosphere.

First couple of dinners were okay acceptable but it get worse and worse. Services are horrible as the staffs probably are overworked and definitely rude as hell.
Food is small in portion and we ordered a stir fry flat noodle but end up getting a plateful of soaking wet corn-starched filled disgusting paste of white goo. We tried to complain and the staff literally ignore then scold us back thinking we are just a young couple and can be bullied. Fortunately the family next to us helped out and also voice out for us, that dish is unacceptable to anyone.

Fresh 
Delicious 
Reasonable Price
The problem is, we don’t know where to eat  every Thursday....!
Good quality food with fair price best for lunch or quickie
